  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "There are many different kinds of tools for conducting eye tracking research.",
    "First, there are software tools.",
    "Software tools for eye tracking research can be subdivided into at least two categories.",
    "One category consists of complete readyto-use software suites for stimulus presentation that allow recording, visualizing and analyzing eye tracking data, such as Tobii Pro Lab, the SR Research Experiment Builder and Data Viewer bundle, iMotions Lab and EyeTrace (Kübler et al., 2015; Otto et al., 2018).",
    "In contrast to software suites that aim to provide a one-stop solution to all one's research needs stand dedicated software tools that aim to do only one thing and do that well."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "One category consists of complete readyto-use software suites for stimulus presentation that allow recording, visualizing and analyzing eye tracking data, such as Tobii Pro Lab, the SR Research Experiment Builder and Data Viewer bundle, iMotions Lab and EyeTrace (Kübler et al., 2015; Otto et al., 2018)."
  ]
